<!-- ── METHOD ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="g-section" id="method">
  <div class="g-section-inner">
    <div class="g-label reveal">How it works</div>
    <h2 class="g-section-headline reveal">Intelligence with a process.</h2>
    <p class="g-section-sub reveal">We don't aggregate opinions. We build proprietary data pipelines and scoring models — then surface only what moves the needle.</p>
    <div class="g-method-grid">
      <div class="g-method-card reveal">
        <div class="g-method-num">01</div>
        <h3 class="g-method-title">Collect</h3>
        <p class="g-method-body">29 live pipelines ingest crypto prices, on-chain data, FRED macro series, CFTC positioning, and alternative datasets — continuously.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="g-method-card reveal">
        <div class="g-method-num">02</div>
        <h3 class="g-method-title">Score</h3>
        <p class="g-method-body">Proprietary models weight momentum, sentiment, macro correlation, and on-chain signals — then normalize across assets. One signal you can act on.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="g-method-card reveal">
        <div class="g-method-num">03</div>
        <h3 class="g-method-title">Signal</h3>
        <p class="g-method-body">When something materially changes — a trend shifts, funding rates spike, macro data breaks — you hear about it first. That's the signal.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── SIGNAL CARDS ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
