        </div>
        <a href="/dashboard/trading" class="g-signal-cta">View pipeline →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="g-signal-card reveal">
        <div class="g-signal-header">
          <span class="g-signal-category">MACRO</span>
          <span class="g-signal-badge neutral">Rate Watch</span>
        </div>
        <div class="g-signal-body">
          <p class="g-signal-headline">Fed holds at 5.25–5.50% — crypto correlations shifting as rate expectations reprice</p>
